<! [CDATA[
Mu Space Logo
mu Space and Advanced Technology Co., Ltd., operating under the name mu Space Corp, is an aerospace manufacturer and satellite internet service provider in South East Asia. The company was founded by James Yenbamroong in 2017, with the goal to deliver cutting-edge technology products along with developing aerospace technology and telecommunications service in the region. The company started with a registered capital of US$3 million. In December 2017, Thailand’s National Broadcasting and Telecommunications Commission granted mu Space a 15-year license to provide satellite services in the country until the year 2032.
You can download theMu Spacelogo on full-version of the page.
